ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectLoran-A Equipment Loan 1966 Termination of Treaty (US) #4
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to terminate for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between Canada and the United States of America concerning the loan by the United States of Loran-A equipment in addition to that loaned under the Agreement of June 8, 1965, done on 19 April and 28 July 1966.
